name: Amalan Iyengar
tagline: Here you can read all my ramblings and my unfinished math programming projects
body:
### Welcome to my page

Hi! I am Amalan Iyengar, a junior at East Chapel Hill High School. I like programming in Dart and Typescript, since Javascript kinda sucks. I'll probably add more later, but for now, here are links to some of my projects. Looking back at them, all I can think is "what was I doing?"

* [Symbolic differentiator](Javascript-CAS)
* [Truth Table generator](Truth-tables)
* [Graphing library](graph.js)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
